<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" class="page">
{{> head title="Focus Frame"}}

<body class="page__body">

  <div class="site-container">

    {{> header page="home"}}

    <main class="main">
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="hero__inner">
            <div class="hero__content">
              <h1 class="hero__title">
                Discover the magic <br> of <span class="colored-text">photography</span> in our school
              </h1>
              <p>
                Our photography school offers an unforgettable journey, where you can learn the basics of composition,
                master technical skills, translate your unique ideas.
              </p>

              <div class="hero__interaction">
                <div class="hero__students">
                  <ul>
                    <li>
                      <img src="./images/students1.png" alt="image of students" width="54" height="54">
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      <img src="./images/students3.png" alt="image of students" width="54" height="54">
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      <img src="./images/students2.png" alt="image of students" width="54" height="54">
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                  <p>Our happy <br>
                    students
                    <img src="./icons/arrow.svg">
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="hero__reviews">
                  <img src="./icons/circle.svg">
                  <div>
                    <p>
                      Reviews
                    </p>
                    <span>
                      +1500
                    </span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hero__image">
              <img src="./images/hero.png" alt="hero image" width="400" height="520">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="marquee section">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>
            <span class="colored-text">Master</span> your photography skills <span class="colored-text">with us!</span>
          </h2>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section id="about" class="about section">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>
            About <span class="colored-text">Us</span>
          </h2>
          <div class="about__inner">
            <div class="about__img">
              <img src="./images/about.png" alt=" image of camera" width="560" height="240">
            </div>

            <div class="about__descr">
              <p>Our photography school is designed to teach you everything you need to know about this magical art.
                Regardless of your experience or skill level, we offer a wide range of courses to suit your needs and
                interests. Our teaching team consists of experienced photographers who have many years of experience in
                this field. They strive not only to share their knowledge, but also to inspire you to develop and
                express your unique creativity.</p>

              <p>
                Our courses cover a wide range of topics, from the basics of photography and equipment use to
                professional image processing and creating impressive compositions. You will have the opportunity to
                learn the technical aspects of photography, discover your own style and develop your own visual
                language.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </section>

      <section id="course" class="course section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="course__inner">
            <div class="course__descr">
              <h2>
                Our <span class="colored-text">Courses</span>
              </h2>
              <p>
                At our photography school, we offer a variety of courses that cover all aspects of this fascinating
                art.
                Regardless of your experience or skill level, we have courses to suit your needs and goals.
              </p>
            </div>

            <ul class="course__list">
              <li class="course__item">
                <h3>
                  Basics of <br>photography
                </h3>
                <p>
                  During this course, you will be able to familiarize yourself with different types of cameras, learn
                  the basics of composition.
                </p>
              </li>

              <li class="course__item">
                <h3>
                  Landscape <br>photography
                </h3>
                <p>
                  In this course, you'll learn how to choose the right angles, frame landscapes, and create depth and
                  perspective in your images.
                </p>
              </li>

              <li class="course__item">
                <h3>
                  Portrait <br>
                  photography
                </h3>
                <p>
                  During this course, you will learn to choose the right lighting, reproduce the mood and expressions
                  on the faces of the models.
                </p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="mentors" class="mentors section">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>
            Our <span class="colored-text">Mentors</span>
          </h2>

          <ul class="mentors__list">
            <li class="mentors__item">
              <img src="./images/mentors/emilia-smith.png" alt="image of emilia smith" width="180" height="180">
              <h3>
                Emilia Smith
              </h3>
              <p>
                1.5 years of experience
              </p>
            </li>

            <li class="mentors__item">
              <img src="./images/mentors/alex-lebedev.png" alt="image of alex lebedev" width="180" height="180">
              <h3>
                Alex Lebedev
              </h3>
              <p>
                3.5 years of experience
              </p>
            </li>

            <li class="mentors__item">
              <img src="./images/mentors/mia-dubrovska.png" alt="image of mia dubrovska" width="180" height="180">
              <h3>
                Mia Dubrovska
              </h3>
              <p>
                2.0 years of experience
              </p>
            </li>

            <li class="mentors__item">
              <img src="./images/mentors/eliot-kovalev.png" alt="image of eliot kovalev" width="180" height="180">
              <h3>
                Eliot Kovalev
              </h3>
              <p>
                4.0 years of experience
              </p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="sign" class="sign section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="sign__inner">
            <div class="sign__content">
              <h2>
                Sign <span class="colored-text">Up</span>
              </h2>
              <p>
                Please use the form below to contact us. Enter your name, email, and message and we'll get back to you
                shortly.
              </p>
              <form class="sign__form">
                <label><input type="text" class="sign__input" placeholder="Enter your name" required></label>
                <label><input type="email" class="sign__input" placeholder="Enter your email" required></label>
                <label><textarea class="sign__input sign__input--textarea " placeholder="Message" rows="5"
                    required></textarea></label>
                <button class="btn" type="submit">send</button>
                <p class="sign__policy">
                  By clicking on "Send" button, you agree to our <a href="#" class="sign__link">Privacy Policy</a>, <br>
                  and
                  allow Promodo to use this information for marketing purposes.
                </p>
              </form>
            </div>

            <div class="sign__images">
              <div class="sign__img sign__img--small">
                <img src="./images/small-camera.png" alt="image of small camera" width="155" height="165">
              </div>
              <div class="sign__img ">
                <img src="./images/big-camera.png" alt="image of big camera" width="255" height="315">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="reviews" class="reviews section">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>
            Reviews
          </h2>
          <ul class="reviews__list">
            <li class="reviews__item">
              <div class="reviews__content">
                <div class="reviews__avatar">
                  <img src="./images/abraham-baker.png" alt="Abraham Baker" width="56" height="56">
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="reviews__name">Abraham Baker</h3>
                    <p class="reviews__role">Student</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="reviews__stars">
                  <img src="./images/stars.png" alt="rating 4.5 stars" class="reviews__stars">
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="reviews__text">
                I am very pleased that I decided to enroll in photography school. The teachers turned out to be very
                talented and experienced professionals who share their knowledge and are dedicated to their work. I was
                able to expand my skills and discover my own style.
              </p>
            </li>

            <li class="reviews__item">
              <div class="reviews__content">
                <div class="reviews__avatar">
                  <img src="./images/amanda-lowery.png" alt="Amanda Lowery" width="56" height="56">
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="reviews__name">Amanda Lowery</h3>
                    <p class="reviews__role">Student</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="reviews__stars">
                  <img src="./images/stars.png" alt="rating 4.5 stars" class="reviews__stars">
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="reviews__text">
                The courses at the photography school exceeded all my expectations. I gained not only technical
                knowledge, but also inspiration and motivation to reach new heights in my creativity. Hands-on classes
                and workshops helped me understand different styles of photography.
              </p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

    </main>

    {{> footer}}

  </div>


</body>

</html>